# ApiSources Module

## Overview

API Source Configuration supports multi-provider LLM management with auto-detection and model tiers

## Goals

- **G1** — API Source Configuration supports multi-provider LLM management with auto-detection and model tiers
- **G2** — APIs Documentation View

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — API Source & Multi-Provider Architecture
- **A2** — APIs Documentation View Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — API Source Configuration
- **D2** — APIs Documentation View

